      "description": "Classic 3-inch pocket design that allows the rod to slide through for a seamless fit. Provides a soft, gathered appearance for a cozy and effortless window treatment."
    },
    {
      "name": "back tap",
      "price": "45",
      "fullness": "200%",
      "image": "//luxdrape.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/back_tab.jpg?crop=center&height=108&v=1745829308&width=108",
      "description": "Hidden tabs at the back create a clean, tailored look without visible hardware. Combines the ease of a rod pocket with the structured elegance of a pleated finish."
    },
    {
      "name": "top tap",
      "price": "45",
      "fullness": "200%",
      "image": "//luxdrape.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/tabtop.jpg?crop=center&height=108&v=1745829208&width=108",
      "description": "Evenly spaced 4-inch tabs designed for easy installation directly onto the curtain rod. Creates a casual, relaxed atmosphere ideal for both indoor and outdoor living spaces."
    },
    {
      "name": "flat hook",
      "price": "45",
      "fullness": "200%",
